content:
I made yesterday tweets that may appear critical.

Let me also throw some praise.

Cape Town is pretty clean and garbage collection seems to work very well. The water supply is safe to drink (seems it rained well this year), electricity supply works *almost* 24/7.

It works.

4/n https://t.co/z0NTJK4Vdn
